### 获取科室列表
GET http://localhost:8082/api/departments
Accept: application/json

### 获取指定科室和日期的医生排班列表
# 注意: 请将 departmentId 和 date 替换为实际要查询的值
GET http://localhost:8082/api/registration/doctors?departmentId=DEP013&date=2025-11-15
Accept: application/json

### 获取医生详细信息
# 注意: 请将 "doc-1" 替换为实际要查询的医生ID
GET http://localhost:8082/api/doctors/doc-1
Accept: application/json

### 创建挂号
# 注意: 请将 patientId 和 scheduleRecordId 替换为实际存在的ID
POST http://localhost:8082/api/registrations
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "patientId": "PAT0100",
  "scheduleRecordId": "SCH1003",
  "confirm": true
}

### 取消挂号（删除之前添加的记录）
# 注意: 如已修改上面的 patientId / scheduleRecordId，这里也需要同步修改
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/registrations?patientId=PAT0100&scheduleRecordId=SCH1003
Accept: application/json
